  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #e74c3c;font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Following the AI classification update, there are no changes in the thresholds and quality process.</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Jump to:</strong></span></p>\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#T1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>What are the benefits of selling Premium devices?</strong></a></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"#T2\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\">What devices can be sold as Premium grade?</a></strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"#T3\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\">What are the requirements to be eligible to sell Premium grade devices? </a></strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#track\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;\"><strong>How to track the quality results of the Premium offer? </strong></span></a></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"#T4\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\">What are the specific warranty and applicable after-sales conditions for Premium grade devices?</a></strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"#T5\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\">What are the specific quality standards for Premium grade devices?</a></strong></span><br><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;color: #2980b9;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"#T7\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;text-decoration: underline;\">Can I be exited from the Premium grade program? </a></strong></span></div>\n<div> </div>\n<h2><a id=\"T1\" name=\"T1\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What are the benefits of selling Premium grade devices?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quality is the primary reason why customers hesitate to buy refurbished devices. With the Premium grade program, customers will have access to the best quality devices proven to deliver best-in-class performance and longevity. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Selling Premium devices will help you sell more products (around 10-15%) and at a price +10–15% higher than Excellent grade, as customers will cover the higher-quality costs. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><a id=\"T2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What devices can be sold as Premium grade?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Premium devices follow high quality requirements: </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Excellent appearance condition with flawless screens and barely visible scratches on the bodies (not visible at arm&#39;s length),</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Only official manufacturer (genuine) spare parts,</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">“Open-box” (following a change of mind) and unopened devices (demo devices for instance),</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">A battery capacity of at least 90% (as shown in the device and/or test reports) and less than 500 cycle counts. Devices with reprogrammed or booster batteries can’t be sold as Premium grade.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For MacBooks:</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Only ISO keyboard</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Power delivery chargers/cables (and magsafe to USB-C cable for MagSafe 3 enabled devices)</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Premium devices are typically as-is stock (for Apple devices) </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Repaired devices can be sold as Premium only if the repair was performed by a manufacturer-approved repair partner (using official manufacturer parts and following manufacturer procedures). If a device’s repair status can’t be guaranteed, the device must be listed as Excellent.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Charger cables have to be original or MFI certified, when applicable.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><a id=\"T3\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What are the requirements to be eligible to sell Premium grade devices? </span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">As each customer pays more  to buy a Premium smartphone, high quality is critical. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Only sellers complying with high quality standards (as defined below) will be able to sell Premium grade devices.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.8;text-align: justify;background-color: #f9f9f9;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 18pt;\"> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border: none rgb(0, 0, 0);width: 62.9562%;height: 319.913px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 33.3416%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 24.069%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 21.307%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 21.307%;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 41.5972px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.46875pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\">EU</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\"></span></strong></span></td><td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.46875pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\">Onboarding Thresholds</span></strong></span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 36.3194px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;background-color: #f9f9f9;border: 0.46875pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.999997pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;color: #111111;\">Smartphones</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.999997pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;color: #111111;\">iPads</sp