>No recent failed MO</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"track\" target=\"_blank\"></a> How to track the quality results of the Premium Offer? </span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In your Back Office, follow the tabs: Insights &gt; Quality<br>Once your Quality Insights Dashboard is open, select the condition filter and choose “Premium”<br>You can apply this filter both on the overview page and within the detailed views for Long-Term Defective and Appearance.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a id=\"T4\" target=\"_blank\"></a></strong>What are the specific warranty and applicable after-sales conditions for Premium grade devices?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">All after-sales conditions of regular products sold on Back Market apply to Premium grade devices. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In addition, the following conditions apply: </span></p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If the origin of a single part can’t be guaranteed and your customer receives a warning message about an uncertified part, your customer is entitled to a refund or replacement, at your cost.</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If a battery falls below 89% during the cancellation period (change of mind), your customer will be offered a refund or replacement, at your cost</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If a battery falls below 85% after the cancellation period (change of mind) and within 1 year of purchase, your customer will be offered a repair or replacement, at your cost.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a id=\"T5\" target=\"_blank\"></a></strong>What are the specific quality standards for Premium grade devices?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quality KPIs apply to Premium-grade devices sold on the Back Market platform. If you do not meet these thresholds, you will enter an alert period and will have two months to improve your performance. Failure to meet the required standards within this timeframe will result in suspension from the program for a minimum of three months. After this period, you must re-apply and demonstrate compliance with all the requirements outlined above.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border: none;width: 60.1059%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 36.1666%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 22.7391%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 22.9342%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 18.1866%;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 18.75pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.999997pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\">EU</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: bottom;border: 0.999997pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\">Run Thresholds</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;color: #000000;\"></span></strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 15.75pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 0.999997p